{"tid":1064366,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(家長都有假，估國家食品）【發霉】假家長開記者會 真家長被警員包圍","createTime":"2019-03-16T13:04:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-16T16:14:22.000Z","uid":22675,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d39264538ab71db134ff5a1672df31c7655ff88c","tid":1064366,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T13:04:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190316/large/1552726379_1bbf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190316%2Flarge%2F1552726379_1bbf.jpg&h=7710cb31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n四川省成都市第七中學實驗學校的食堂，被家長揭發使用發霉、腐爛的食物給學生食用，引致學生腹瀉、便血，事件引發全國關注。當局公佈食物檢驗結果，反而引起更大質疑，當局同時大力控制家長，有家長更稱當局找來「10幾車的假家長」，讓他們在新聞發佈會上露面，真的家長則被大批警員重重包圍，禁止他們公開維權。<br />\n<br />\n「電視上說的都是假家長，要代表我們開新聞發佈會！」在四川省成都市第七中學實驗學校門外的學生家長，被警察重重包圍。家長透露，自從揭發食堂用發霉、腐爛食物以後，當局不斷打壓家長維權。有家長稱，當局已經掌握他們家人的姓名、電話、地址等，有家長稱自稱「社區工作人員」的人直接闖到其家中，要「了解訴求」，但家長稱當局的目的十分明顯。<br />\n<br />\n廣告<br />\n<br />\n即使家長希望收起憤怒的情緒、希望派出代表與官員談判，但當局在學校的外圍部署30多部警車，警員將家長們重重包圍，附近的手機發射站亦關閉，禁止他們維權，更讓家長們悲憤的，是網上出現大量污衊家長的消息，例如家長在校園內吸煙、在操場內大聲叫罵、亂闖女生宿舍、到食堂檢驗飯菜等等，有家長發文批評：「彌補和糾錯就那麼難嗎？政府還在鎮壓刪除、顛倒是非黑白，為了保全自己的烏紗帽！」<br />\n<br />\n事件已經引起中央關注，教育部副部長鍾登華今日在全國校園食品安全工作電視電話會議上宣佈，國務院領導關注事件，並已作出多次批示；國家市場監管總局局長張茅則稱，目前「問題還沒有最後查清」，他要求全國各地排查學校食品安全的風險隱患。<br />\n<br />\n新浪微博/《新京報》"},{"pid":"2c068837c5b545fcca7205ab73d813cb3cea683f","tid":1064366,"uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T13:05:13.000Z","msg":"(家長都有假，估國家）【發霉<span style=\"color: red;\">食品</span>】假家長開記者會 真家長被警員包圍<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190316/59375954\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190316%2F59375954&d=WPnlDqr2f%2BBS7HOcP0JQk9WqQ%2Br5Wu6dnGlIIIMUdw0%3D&h=284bb3e0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190316%2F59375954&h=0c0ff993\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190316/59375954</a>"},{"pid":"03a3fddfbec9ad0085ef6d3acb48aa178b1da8cb","tid":1064366,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T13:08:33.000Z","msg":"抵撚死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e31c0b99bc1c099520614393516de11e7218d8a2","tid":1064366,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T13:09:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a37551ae455ef7bb338c573a6fb25a2bf9cfc2cd","tid":1064366,"uid":191926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T13:10:19.000Z","msg":"狗屎垃圾國家<br />\n<br />\n連登班支那垃圾再吹奏<br />\n都狗也不屌<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36b9758091c1e3dca397df35f6ffe6c71c2831e3","tid":1064366,"uid":124410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T13:12:02.000Z","msg":"乜都係假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"327f38952dd0d45595c386b88b88d4eeeeb4ed02","tid":1064366,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T13:34:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bb8a9c23558853d1406b4b3d002d69669c2251e","tid":1064366,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T13:39:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a6eedddd2b3f4d8898eca1bf935c9c9a43fcd71","tid":1064366,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T14:20:49.000Z","